gameRecap.title: Game Recap: Pacers 140, Raptors 123
gameRecap.excerpt: The Pacers defeated the Raptors, 140-123. Tyrese Haliburton recorded 30 points, five rebounds, and five assists for the Pacers, while Obi Toppin added 23 points, six rebounds, and two assists in the victory. RJ Barrett tallied 23 points, four rebounds, and four assists for the Raptors in the losing effort. The Pacers improve to 46-34, while the Raptors fall to 25-54.
